Package: MLBscrapeR
Type: Package
Title: Scrape Baseball teams and players statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zeyu Li
Maintainer: Zeyu Li <lizeyu@umich.edu>
Description: This package scrapes statistics of active baseball teams and of their players from "http://www.baseball-reference.com/". The package provides two functions: one scrapes a list of players on a given baseball team; the other scrapes an individual player's statistics on a given baseball team in a specified area. The package contains a lookup table of active baseball teams' names.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
imports:
    stringr 
    stringdist
    xml2
    rvest
Suggests: testthat
